Here are quick ways to click #submit-button depending on your environment.

- Browser console / plain JS:
  const btn = document.querySelector('#submit-button'); if (btn) btn.click(); else console.error('No element found');

- jQuery:
  $('#submit-button').click();

- Puppeteer (Node):
  await page.click('#submit-button');

- Playwright (Node):
  await page.click('#submit-button');

- Selenium (Python):
  from selenium.webdriver.common.by import By
  driver.find_element(By.CSS_SELECTOR, '#submit-button').click()

- Selenium (JS):
  await driver.findElement({ css: '#submit-button' }).click();

- Cypress:
  cy.get('#submit-button').click();

